text: Meral Izabelle Tasbas (born 4 April 1979) is a Swedish television star, singer and actress. She is best known for her appearances in five seasons of the reality series The Bar. She appeared on it between the years of 2000 and 2004 on TV3. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish actors Category:Swedish singers Category:Reality television participants
